about this one.

30:34.416 --> 30:35.996
It's a classic case...

30:36.835 --> 30:39.665
Of what is and isn't real...

30:40.589 --> 30:41.839
In the mind...

30:42.924 --> 30:46.014
Of a boy... named Walter.

30:47.596 --> 30:49.136
Perception?

30:50.640 --> 30:52.180
Reality?

30:53.685 --> 30:55.225
Walter.

31:50.117 --> 31:51.907
All right, everybody,
take your seats.

31:58.917 --> 32:01.497
<i>Okay, we have a new student
joining us today.</i>

32:01.503 --> 32:04.713
