42:30.006 --> 42:31.376
Don't say nothin'.

42:41.225 --> 42:42.385
Well, why are you
just standing there?

42:42.393 --> 42:43.833
Why the hell didn't you
get the door?

42:44.353 --> 42:45.443
Who's that?

42:46.481 --> 42:48.571
That's just one
of Walter's teachers.

42:48.941 --> 42:50.361
He was just leaving.

42:54.155 --> 42:55.735
Is there a problem?

42:55.740 --> 42:56.780
No.

42:56.783 --> 42:59.703
Actually, he just came over
to drop off some homework.

43:01.120 --> 43:02.870
Actually, sir,
now that you mention it...

43:03.206 --> 43:06.416
Walter does seem to be having
a few small problems...

43:06.584 --> 43:09.594
That might deserve
some looking into.

43:23.518 --> 43:25.348
<i>Well, Walter's only been
at this school</i>

43:25.353 --> 43:26.563
<i>for a couple of weeks...</i>

43:26.979 --> 43:29.439
And he does have trouble
making friends.

43:29.857 --> 43:33.107
So what kind of problem
are we talking about?

43:35.279 --> 43:37.569
Well, aside from the bruises...

43:38.366 --> 43:39.446
Aside from that...

43:39.617 --> 43:43.077
There's, uh, this monster
that he says is in the house.

43:43.663 --> 43:46.373
He seems very disturbed by it.

43:46.374 --> 43:48.464
In fact, he's even
drawn a picture...

43:48.626 --> 43:50.126
Of the monster.

43:59.512 --> 44:03.772
He, uh, thinks he needs
to kill the monster.

44:04.517 --> 44:08.147
I mean, he...
He really believes it.

44:12.733 --> 44:13.903
I'll talk to him.

44:14.902 --> 44:17.282
That's it?
You'll just talk to him?

44:19.532 --> 44:22.332
I will talk to him.

44:28.666 --> 44:29.916
Okay.

44:32.211 --> 44:35.631
Sissy, would you show him
to the door, please?

44:42.305 --> 44:43.675
Thanks for the tea.

45:04.452 --> 45:05.832
Go to your room.

45:13.628 --> 45:15.088
- Miss Johnson...
- Go!

45:57.755 --> 45:58.875
Walter!

45:59.423 --> 46:01.593
You little motherfucker.

46:02.385 --> 46:05.715
You like to draw fucked-up
pictures of people, huh?

46:09.767 --> 46:10.767
Huh?

46:10.810 --> 46:11.940
Carl, no!

46:29.328 --> 46:31.748
