47:01.569 --> 47:02.569
<i>Miss Johnson!</i>

47:02.611 --> 47:04.361
Your little ass is mine!

47:04.905 --> 47:06.565
Oh, you gonna draw a picture
of somebody

47:06.574 --> 47:07.994
and make them look
like a monster?

47:07.995 --> 47:10.912
But you think
that shit is funny? Huh?

47:11.954 --> 47:13.504
<i>- Get up!
- Miss Johnson!</i>

47:15.166 --> 47:17.666
- You okay?
- He's gonna kill him.

47:17.668 --> 47:18.838
- No!
- Wait! Wait... here.

47:19.045 --> 47:20.045
<i>Wait here!</i>

47:20.171 --> 47:21.171
Mom.

47:23.007 --> 47:24.667
Carl, stop it!
Just take it easy!

47:24.675 --> 47:27.085
Take it easy? This ain't
your motherfuckin' house!

47:29.347 --> 47:30.427
No!

47:46.739 --> 47:49.159
- Take it easy.
- Motherfucker!

47:59.794 --> 48:01.134
No!

48:03.756 --> 48:05.166
'Get "no!"

48:05.549 --> 48:06.839
I'm not through with this yet!

48:09.762 --> 48:11.222
Come <i>here!</i> Come here.

48:11.597 --> 48:13.597
<i>- What's it gonna be?
- Let me go!</i>

48:16.477 --> 48:18.517
Motherfucker!

48:21.649 --> 48:22.979
Have you lost your mind?

48:22.983 --> 48:25.033
I see you ain't the only one
need an ass-whoopin'!

48:26.112 --> 48:27.112
Bitch!

48:54.432 --> 48:57.272
This shit ain't over yet, bitch.

49:03.858 --> 49:05.278
