49:21.876 --> 49:23.126
What are we gonna do?

49:24.170 --> 49:26.630
<i>They find him here like this,
no one's gonna believe us.</i>

49:29.175 --> 49:30.215
Don't worry.

49:33.304 --> 49:35.684
