50:41.205 --> 50:43.955
So dead motherfuckers be
playin' with dolls now, right?

50:43.958 --> 50:46.288
Yes. But this doll...

50:46.919 --> 50:50.209
It's a way station
for lost souls.

50:50.923 --> 50:52.473
- What?
- Sometimes...

50:52.633 --> 50:55.263
When a person's body
has been through a lot...

50:56.053 --> 50:58.063
