for the soul to survive...

51:04.979 --> 51:06.769
Until it can move on.

51:07.398 --> 51:10.275
Man, you for real?

51:10.276 --> 51:11.486
<i>Yes!</i>

51:13.737 --> 51:15.357
I found this doll...

51:16.448 --> 51:19.368
In a house in the south.

51:20.869 --> 51:24.829
It is an amazing thing.

51:30.546 --> 51:32.626
<i>You can give it
any name you want.</i>

51:32.840 --> 51:37.260
<i>The fact is, affirmative action,
quotas, reparations...</i>

51:37.261 --> 51:39.101
<i>All mean one thing...</i>

51:40.264 --> 51:44.100
<i>Another qualified individual
won't get a job...</i>

51:44.101 --> 51:45.691
Or an education...

51:45.894 --> 51:48.944
<i>Simply because
he's not the right color.</i>

51:52.526 --> 51:55.316
<i>I thought that's what we were
trying to get away from.</i>

51:55.779 --> 51:57.409
<i>Duke Metger for governor.</i>

51:57.698 --> 51:59.368
<i>An original American.</i>

51:59.700 --> 52:01.490
<i>Isn't it about time?</i>

52:02.328 --> 52:04.908
That's great.
I'd even vote for me.

52:05.331 --> 52:07.081
Listen, by the time
I finish with you...

52:07.333 --> 52:09.671
You might even get
a few black votes in the till.

52:09.672 --> 52:11.127
Well, a start would be

52:11.128 --> 52:13.208
